<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Nexus — Web Design & AI Automation</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;1,9..40,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

:root {
  --black: #050505;
  --white: #f5f3ef;
  --off-white: #e8e4dc;
  --cream: #d4cfc4;
  --gray-400: #8a8680;
  --gray-600: #4a4845;
  --gray-900: #0d0c0b;
  --gold: #c8a96e;
  --gold-dim: rgba(200,169,110,0.12);
  --gold-glow: rgba(200,169,110,0.25);
  --surface: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  --surface-2: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  --border: rgba(200,169,110,0.12);
  --border-strong: rgba(200,169,110,0.25);
}

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  background: var(--black);
  color: var(--white);
  overflow-x: hidden;
  line-height: 1.6;
  cursor: none;
}

/* CUSTOM CURSOR */
.cursor {
  width: 8px; height: 8px;
  background: var(--gold);
  border-radius: 50%;
  position: fixed;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 9999;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  transition: transform 0.1s, width 0.3s, height 0.3s, opacity 0.3s;
  mix-blend-mode: normal;
}
.cursor-ring {
  width: 36px; height: 36px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.4);
  border-radius: 50%;
  position: fixed;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 9998;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  transition: transform 0.15s ease-out, width 0.3s, height 0.3s;
}
.cursor.hover { width: 14px; height: 14px; }
.cursor-ring.hover { width: 56px; height: 56px; border-color: var(--gold); }

/* GRAIN OVERLAY */
body::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed; inset: 0;
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='1'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  opacity: 0.025;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 1000;
}

/* NAV */
nav {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 24px 56px;
  transition: all 0.4s;
}
nav.scrolled {
  background: rgba(5,5,5,0.92);
  backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 18px 56px;
}
.nav-logo {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  text-decoration: none; color: var(--white);
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
}
.logo-n {
  width: 34px; height: 34px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), rgba(200,169,110,0.6));
  border-radius: 8px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 17px; font-weight: 900; color: #050505;
}
.nav-links {
  display: flex; gap: 40px; list-style: none;
}
.nav-links a {
  color: var(--gray-400); text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  transition: color 0.2s; cursor: none;
}
.nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { color: var(--white); }
.nav-cta {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--gold); border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
  padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  cursor: none; transition: all 0.25s;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.nav-cta:hover {
  background: var(--gold-dim);
  border-color: var(--gold);
  color: var(--gold);
}

/* SECTIONS */
section { padding: 120px 56px; max-width: 1240px; margin: 0 auto; }

/* HERO */
.hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 140px 56px 100px;
  max-width: none;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.hero-bg {
  position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none;
}
.hero-bg::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -20%; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
  width: 800px; height: 800px;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(200,169,110,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
}
.hero-bg::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(200,169,110,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(200,169,110,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 80px 80px;
  mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 30%, black, transparent);
}

.hero-eyebrow {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 2.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 48px;
  opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.2s ease forwards;
}
.eyebrow-line {
  width: 40px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); opacity: 0.6;
}

.hero-title {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(52px, 7vw, 96px);
  font-weight: 800; line-height: 0.95;
  letter-spacing: -3px;
  max-width: 900px;
  opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.35s ease forwards;
}
.hero-title em {
  font-style: normal;
  color: transparent;
  -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(200,169,110,0.5);
}
.hero-title .gold { color: var(--gold); -webkit-text-stroke: 0; }

.hero-sub {
  font-size: 17px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--gray-400);
  max-width: 500px; margin: 40px 0 56px;
  line-height: 1.8;
  opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.5s ease forwards;
}

.hero-ctas {
  display: flex; gap: 16px;
  opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.65s ease forwards;
}

.btn-primary {
  background: var(--gold);
  color: #050505; border: none;
  padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px;
  cursor: none; transition: all 0.25s;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.btn-primary:hover {
  background: #d4b57a;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(200,169,110,0.25);
}

.btn-ghost {
  background: transparent; color: var(--cream);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px;
  cursor: none; transition: all 0.25s;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.btn-ghost:hover {
  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  background: var(--surface);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

/* MARQUEE */
.marquee-wrap {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 20px 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-top: 100px;
  position: relative;
  opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1s 0.8s ease forwards;
}
.marquee-track {
  display: flex; gap: 0;
  animation: marquee 30s linear infinite;
  width: max-content;
}
.marquee-item {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 32px;
  padding: 0 48px;
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-600);
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.marquee-dot {
  width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--gold); opacity: 0.5;
}
@keyframes marquee {
  from { transform: translateX(0); }
  to { transform: translateX(-50%); }
}

/* STATS ROW */
.stats-row {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 2px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-top: 0;
}
.stat-item {
  padding: 40px 36px;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  transition: background 0.3s;
}
.stat-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
.stat-item:hover { background: var(--gold-dim); }
.stat-num {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 42px; font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: -2px; color: var(--white);
  line-height: 1;
}
.stat-num span { color: var(--gold); }
.stat-label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-600); margin-top: 8px; font-weight: 300; }

/* LABEL TAG */
.label-tag {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 2.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.label-tag::before {
  content: ''; width: 24px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); opacity: 0.6;
}

.section-title {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 56px);
  font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.05;
  letter-spacing: -2px; margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.section-sub {
  font-size: 16px; color: var(--gray-400);
  max-width: 460px; line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 72px; font-weight: 300;
}

/* SERVICES */
.services-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1px; background: var(--border);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.service-card {
  background: #0a0908;
  padding: 48px 40px;
  transition: background 0.4s;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.service-card::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
  transform: scaleX(0); transition: transform 0.4s;
}
.service-card:hover { background: rgba(200,169,110,0.04); }
.service-card:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }

.service-num {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px;
  color: var(--gold); opacity: 0.6; margin-bottom: 32px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.service-card h3 {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;
  letter-spacing: -0.5px; line-height: 1.2;
}
.service-card p {
  font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-400); line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 32px; font-weight: 300;
}
.service-features { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
.service-features li {
  font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-600);
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
}
.service-features li::before {
  content: '';
  width: 12px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); opacity: 0.5; flex-shrink: 0;
}

/* BEFORE / AFTER */
.ba-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 60px 1fr;
  gap: 0; align-items: stretch;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  margin-top: 64px;
}
.ba-card {
  padding: 48px;
}
.ba-card.before { background: #080706; }
.ba-card.after { background: rgba(200,169,110,0.04); border-left: 1px solid var(--border); }
.ba-divider {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  background: var(--gold-dim);
  border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.ba-arrow {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 20px; color: var(--gold);
  writing-mode: vertical-rl;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
}
.ba-tag {
  font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase; padding: 6px 12px;
  border: 1px solid; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 24px;
  border-radius: 2px;
}
.ba-tag.b { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: var(--gray-600); }
.ba-tag.a { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }
.ba-title {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; letter-spacing: -0.5px;
}
.ba-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-400); margin-bottom: 32px; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 300; }
.metric-row {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
  padding: 14px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.metric-label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-400); flex: 1; font-weight: 300; }
.metric-value { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; }
.metric-value.bad { color: #d4756b; }
.metric-value.good { color: #7db88f; }

/* CASES */
.cases-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
.case-card {
  background: #0a0908; padding: 40px 36px;
  transition: background 0.3s; cursor: none;
  position: relative;
}
.case-card:hover { background: rgba(200,169,110,0.04); }
.case-industry {
  font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); opacity: 0.7;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.case-card h3 {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; letter-spacing: -0.3px;
}
.case-card p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-400); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 32px; font-weight: 300; }
.case-metrics { display: flex; gap: 28px; }
.case-metric .num {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 30px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -1px; color: var(--gold);
}
.case-metric .desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray-600); margin-top: 2px; }

/* PROCESS */
.process-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.process-item {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
  gap: 40px; padding: 40px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  transition: all 0.3s;
}
.process-item:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
.process-item:hover { padding-left: 16px; }
.process-num {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 1px;
  padding-top: 4px;
}
.process-content h3 {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: -0.3px;
}
.process-content p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-400); line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 300; }

/* TESTIMONIALS */
.testimonials-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
.testimonial-card {
  background: #0a0908; padding: 40px 36px;
  transition: background 0.3s;
}
.testimonial-card:hover { background: rgba(200,169,110,0.03); }
.t-stars { color: var(--gold); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 3px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.t-text {
  font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--cream);
  font-weight: 300; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.t-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
.t-avatar {
  width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--gold-dim); border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold);
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
}
.t-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }
.t-biz { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray-600); margin-top: 2px; }

/* TEAM */
.team-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
.team-card {
  background: #0a0908; padding: 40px 36px;
  transition: background 0.3s;
}
.team-card:hover { background: rgba(200,169,110,0.03); }
.team-avatar {
  width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--gold-dim); border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.team-name {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; letter-spacing: -0.3px;
}
.team-role { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.team-bio { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-400); line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 300; }

/* ABOUT */
.about-split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 100px; align-items: center; }
.about-stat { margin-bottom: 32px; padding-bottom: 32px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
.about-stat:last-child { border-bottom: none; margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; }
.about-stat-num {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -2px; color: var(--gold); line-height: 1;
}
.about-stat-label { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-400); margin-top: 6px; font-weight: 300; }

/* CONTACT */
.contact-split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; }
.contact-form-wrap {
  background: #0a0908;
  border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 48px;
}
.form-group { margin-bottom: 24px; }
.form-label {
  display: block; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: var(--gray-400);
  margin-bottom: 10px; text-transform: uppercase;
}
.form-input, .form-select, .form-textarea {
  width: 100%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 14px 18px;
  color: var(--white); font-size: 15px;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  transition: border 0.2s; outline: none;
  border-radius: 2px; font-weight: 300;
}
.form-input:focus, .form-select:focus, .form-textarea:focus {
  border-color: var(--gold); background: var(--gold-dim);
}
.form-select { -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: none; }
.form-textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 120px; }
.form-submit {
  width: 100%; background: var(--gold);
  color: #050505; border: none; padding: 18px;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  cursor: none; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  transition: all 0.25s; text-transform: uppercase;
  border-radius: 2px;
}
.form-submit:hover {
  background: #d4b57a;
  transform: translateY(-1px);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(200,169,110,0.2);
}
.contact-points { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 32px; margin-top: 48px; }
.contact-point { display: flex; gap: 20px; }
.contact-point-icon {
  width: 44px; height: 44px; flex-shrink: 0;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 18px;
}
.contact-point h4 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.contact-point p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-400); line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300; }

/* FINAL CTA */
.final-cta {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 140px 56px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(200,169,110,0.05), transparent);
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.final-cta h2 {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(40px, 5.5vw, 72px);
  font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -2.5px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1;
}
.final-cta p {
  font-size: 17px; color: var(--gray-400); margin-bottom: 52px; font-weight: 300;
}

/* FOOTER */
footer {
  padding: 72px 56px 48px;
  max-width: 1240px; margin: 0 auto;
}
.footer-top {
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: flex-start; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 40px;
  padding-bottom: 56px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.footer-brand p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-400); margin-top: 16px; max-width: 260px; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 300; }
.footer-links { display: flex; gap: 72px; }
.footer-col h4 {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-600); margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.footer-col ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
.footer-col a {
  font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-400); text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.2s; cursor: none; font-weight: 300;
}
.footer-col a:hover { color: var(--white); }
.footer-bottom {
  padding-top: 28px;
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px;
}
.footer-bottom p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-600); font-weight: 300; }

/* PAGE SYSTEM */
.page { display: none; }
.page.active { display: block; }
.nav-links a.active { color: var(--white); }

/* FADE IN */
.fade-in { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease; }
.fade-in.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

/* ANIMATIONS */
@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* PRICING */
.pricing-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
.pricing-card { background: #0a0908; padding: 48px 40px; position: relative; transition: background 0.3s; }
.pricing-card.featured { background: rgba(200,169,110,0.06); }
.pricing-card.featured::before { content: 'Most Popular'; position: absolute; top: -1px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: var(--gold); color: #050505; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 6px 16px; }
.pricing-tier { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 16px; }
.pricing-price { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 52px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -2px; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.pricing-price span { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--gray-400); vertical-align: top; margin-top: 12px; display: inline-block; }
.pricing-period { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-600); margin-bottom: 28px; }
.pricing-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-400); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 32px; font-weight: 300; padding-bottom: 32px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
.pricing-features { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
.pricing-features li { font-size: 14px; color: var(--cream); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-weight: 300; }
.pricing-features li::before { content: '✓'; color: var(--gold); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
.pricing-features li.no { color: var(--gray-600); }
.pricing-features li.no::before { content: '—'; color: var(--gray-600); }
.pricing-btn { width: 100%; padding: 14px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; border-radius: 2px; cursor: none; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; transition: all 0.25s; }
.pricing-btn.outline { background: transparent; color: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border-strong); }
.pricing-btn.outline:hover { background: var(--surface); border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }
.pricing-btn.solid { background: var(--gold); color: #050505; border: none; }
.pricing-btn.solid:hover { background: #d4b57a; transform: translateY(-1px); }

/* FAQ */
.faq-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
.faq-item { background: #0a0908; overflow: hidden; }
.faq-question { padding: 28px 36px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; cursor: none; transition: background 0.2s; gap: 20px; }
.faq-question:hover { background: rgba(200,169,110,0.04); }
.faq-question h4 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.3px; }
.faq-icon { width: 28px; height: 28px; border: 1px solid var(--border-strong); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--gold); font-size: 16px; transition: transform 0.3s; }
.faq-answer { max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.4s ease; }
.faq-answer p { padding: 0 36px 28px; font-size: 15px; color: var(--gray-400); line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 300; }
.faq-item.open .faq-answer { max-height: 300px; }
.faq-item.open .faq-icon { transform: rotate(45deg); border-color: var(--gold); }

/* NOTIFICATION CARDS */
.hero-notifs { position: absolute; right: 80px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; pointer-events: none; }
.notif-card { background: rgba(10,9,8,0.9); border: 1px solid var(--border-strong); padding: 16px 20px; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; backdrop-filter: blur(20px); animation: notifFloat 4s ease-in-out infinite; min-width: 260px; }
.notif-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 1.5s; margin-left: 24px; }
.notif-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 3s; }
.notif-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #6ee7a0; flex-shrink: 0; box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(110,231,160,0.5); animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
.notif-text { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; }
.notif-text strong { display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; }
.notif-text span { color: var(--gray-400); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 300; }
.notif-time { font-size: 11px; color: var(--gray-600); margin-left: auto; white-space: nowrap; }
@keyframes notifFloat { 0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); } 50% { transform: translateY(-6px); } }

/* COUNTER ANIMATION */
.count-num { display: inline-block; }

/* SCROLLBAR */
::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--black); }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(200,169,110,0.2); border-radius: 2px; }

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  nav { padding: 16px 24px; }
  .nav-links { display: none; }
  section { padding: 80px 24px; }
  .hero { padding: 120px 24px 80px; }
  .stats-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .services-grid, .cases-grid, .team-grid, .testimonials-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .contact-split, .about-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  .ba-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .ba-divider { display: none; }
  .footer-links { flex-direction: column; gap: 32px; }
  body { cursor: auto; }
  .cursor, .cursor-ring { display: none; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="mainNav">
  <a class="nav-logo" onclick="showPage('home')" style="cursor:none;">
    <div class="logo-n">N</div>
    Nexus
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a onclick="showPage('home')" class="active" id="nav-home">Home</a></li>
    <li><a onclick="showPage('services')" id="nav-services">Services</a></li>
    <li><a onclick="showPage('results')" id="nav-results">Results</a></li>
    <li><a onclick="showPage('about')" id="nav-about">About</a></li>
    <li><a onclick="showPage('contact')" id="nav-contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
  <button class="nav-cta" onclick="showPage('contact')">Free Audit</button>
</nav>

<!-- ============ HOME PAGE ============ -->
<div class="page active" id="page-home">

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">
      <span class="eyebrow-line"></span>
      Web Design & AI Automation — Sydney, Australia
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      Your website should<br>
      be your best<br>
      <span class="gold">salesperson.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      We build websites and automation systems for local businesses in Australia — so you stop missing leads and start growing.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <button class="btn-primary" onclick="showPage('contact')">Get a Free Audit</button>
      <button class="btn-ghost" onclick="showPage('results')">View Results</button>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-notifs" id="heroNotifs" style="display:none;">
      <div class="notif-card">
        <div class="notif-dot"></div>
        <div class="notif-text"><strong>New lead captured</strong><span>CrossFit South Sydney</span></div>
        <div class="notif-time">just now</div>
      </div>
      <div class="notif-card">
        <div class="notif-dot"></div>
        <div class="notif-text"><strong>Booking confirmed</strong><span>The Fade Room, Melbourne</span></div>
        <div class="notif-time">2m ago</div>
      </div>
      <div class="notif-card">
        <div class="notif-dot"></div>
        <div class="notif-text"><strong>Follow-up sent automatically</strong><span>Apex Property Group</span></div>
        <div class="notif-time">5m ago</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="marquee-wrap">
      <div class="marquee-track">
        <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>Web Design</div>
        <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>AI Automation</div>
        <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>Lead Generation</div>
        <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>Booking Systems</div>
        <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>CRM Integration</div>
        <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>Local SEO</div>
        <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>Sydney, Australia</div>
        <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>Web Design</div>
        <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>AI Automation</div>
        <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>Lead Generation</div>
        <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>Booking Systems</div>
        <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>CRM Integration</div>
        <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>Local SEO</div>
        <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>Sydney, Australia</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <section style="padding-top:80px;padding-bottom:80px;">
    <div class="stats-row fade-in">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num"><span>+37</span>%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Average increase in leads within 60 days</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">2.4<span>×</span></div>
        <div class="stat-label">More bookings from the same traffic</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num"><span>&lt;</span>60s</div>
        <div class="stat-label">How fast your leads get a response</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">3<span>wk</span></div>
        <div class="stat-label">Typical time from brief to launch</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section>
    <div class="fade-in">
      <div class="label-tag">What we do</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">We do three things,<br>and we do them well.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">No fluff, no buzzwords. Just practical systems that bring in more customers.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="services-grid fade-in">
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-num">01 — Web Design</div>
        <h3>Conversion-Focused Web Design</h3>
        <p>High-performance websites engineered to turn visitors into paying customers — not just look good.</p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>Mobile-first, speed-optimized</li>
          <li>Conversion rate optimization</li>
          <li>Professional brand identity</li>
          <li>SEO foundation built-in</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-num">02 — Automation</div>
        <h3>AI Automation Systems</h3>
        <p>Intelligent automation that qualifies leads, books appointments, and follows up — 24/7 without lifting a finger.</p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>AI chatbot & lead capture</li>
          <li>Automated booking flows</li>
          <li>Smart follow-up sequences</li>
          <li>CRM integration</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-num">03 — Growth</div>
        <h3>Lead Generation Systems</h3>
        <p>A full-stack pipeline that attracts, captures, and nurtures your ideal customers into paying clients.</p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>Targeted landing pages</li>
          <li>Lead magnet funnels</li>
          <li>Email & SMS nurture</li>
          <li>Analytics & reporting</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BEFORE / AFTER -->
  <section>
    <div class="fade-in" style="text-align:center;">
      <div class="label-tag" style="justify-content:center;">The transformation</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Before Nexus.<br>After Nexus.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0 auto 0;max-width:480px;">See the difference an intelligent system makes.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ba-grid fade-in">
      <div class="ba-card before">
        <div class="ba-tag b">Before</div>
        <h3 class="ba-title">Generic Website</h3>
        <p class="ba-desc">An outdated brochure site that barely loads on mobile and gives visitors no reason to act.</p>
        <div class="metric-row"><span class="metric-label">Monthly leads</span><span class="metric-value bad">3–5</span></div>
        <div class="metric-row"><span class="metric-label">Mobile speed score</span><span class="metric-value bad">38/100</span></div>
        <div class="metric-row"><span class="metric-label">Missed enquiries</span><span class="metric-value bad">~70%</span></div>
        <div class="metric-row"><span class="metric-label">Response time</span><span class="metric-value bad">24–48 hrs</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="ba-divider">
        <div class="ba-arrow">→</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ba-card after">
        <div class="ba-tag a">After</div>
        <h3 class="ba-title">AI Growth System</h3>
        <p class="ba-desc">A revenue-generating machine that captures, qualifies, and books leads while you sleep.</p>
        <div class="metric-row"><span class="metric-label">Monthly leads</span><span class="metric-value good">40–60</span></div>
        <div class="metric-row"><span class="metric-label">Mobile speed score</span><span class="metric-value good">96/100</span></div>
        <div class="metric-row"><span class="metric-label">Missed enquiries</span><span class="metric-value good">~2%</span></div>
        <div class="metric-row"><span class="metric-label">Response time</span><span class="metric-value good">Under 60 sec</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CASE STUDIES -->
  <section>
    <div class="fade-in">
      <div class="label-tag">Client results</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Real results,<br>real businesses.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">From gyms to clinics — we've built growth systems across every industry.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cases-grid fade-in">
      <div class="case-card" onclick="showPage('results')">
        <div class="case-industry">Fitness & Gym — Sydney</div>
        <h3>CrossFit South Sydney</h3>
        <p>New website + AI booking bot replaced their broken phone system and flooded them with trial sign-ups.</p>
        <div class="case-metrics">
          <div class="case-metric"><div class="num">+52%</div><div class="desc">New members / mo</div></div>
          <div class="case-metric"><div class="num">3.1×</div><div class="desc">Conversion rate</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="case-card" onclick="showPage('results')">
        <div class="case-industry">Barbershop — Melbourne</div>
        <h3>The Fade Room</h3>
        <p>Automated booking and reminder flows eliminated no-shows and freed 15hrs/week of admin time.</p>
        <div class="case-metrics">
          <div class="case-metric"><div class="num">−68%</div><div class="desc">No-show rate</div></div>
          <div class="case-metric"><div class="num">+$8K</div><div class="desc">Monthly revenue</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="case-card" onclick="showPage('results')">
        <div class="case-industry">Real Estate — Brisbane</div>
        <h3>Apex Property Group</h3>
        <p>AI lead qualifier pre-screened enquiries 24/7, tripling the volume of qualified buyer conversations.</p>
        <div class="case-metrics">
          <div class="case-metric"><div class="num">3×</div><div class="desc">Qualified leads</div></div>
          <div class="case-metric"><div class="num">+41%</div><div class="desc">Listings closed</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:40px;" class="fade-in">
      <button class="btn-ghost" onclick="showPage('results')">View All Case Studies →</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
  <section>
    <div class="fade-in">
      <div class="label-tag">Testimonials</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Heard from our clients.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonials-grid fade-in">
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="t-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <div class="t-text">"Honestly didn't expect it to work this well. Within a month we had more trial enquiries than we knew what to do with. The automated follow-ups alone saved us hours every week."</div>
        <div class="t-author">
          <div class="t-avatar">MK</div>
          <div><div class="t-name">Marcus K.</div><div class="t-biz">Gym owner, Western Sydney</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="t-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <div class="t-text">"Our old website was an embarrassment. Mitchell rebuilt it, set up the enquiry system, and now we actually get calls from people who found us online. First time that's ever happened."</div>
        <div class="t-author">
          <div class="t-avatar">SP</div>
          <div><div class="t-name">Sarah P.</div><div class="t-biz">Clinic director, North Shore</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="t-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <div class="t-text">"Was a bit sceptical about the automation stuff but it genuinely works. No-shows are way down and I'm not spending my lunch break chasing up bookings anymore."</div>
        <div class="t-author">
          <div class="t-avatar">DT</div>
          <div><div class="t-name">Dan T.</div><div class="t-biz">Barbershop owner, Melbourne</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING -->
  <section>
    <div class="fade-in">
      <div class="label-tag">Pricing</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">What it costs,<br>what you get.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Prices in AUD. No surprises, no add-ons you didn't ask for.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pricing-grid fade-in">
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="pricing-tier">Starter</div>
        <div class="pricing-price"><span>$</span>1,500</div>
        <div class="pricing-period">one-time project fee</div>
        <div class="pricing-desc">A clean, professional website that actually loads fast and looks good on a phone. Good starting point if you just need to get online properly.</div>
        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li>Custom website (up to 5 pages)</li>
          <li>Mobile-first design</li>
          <li>Contact form setup</li>
          <li>Google Analytics</li>
          <li>2 weeks delivery</li>
          <li class="no">AI automation</li>
          <li class="no">Lead generation funnel</li>
          <li class="no">Ongoing support</li>
        </ul>
        <button class="pricing-btn outline" onclick="showPage('contact')">Get Started</button>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-card featured">
        <div class="pricing-tier">Growth</div>
        <div class="pricing-price"><span>$</span>3,500</div>
        <div class="pricing-period">setup + $350/mo retainer</div>
        <div class="pricing-desc">Website plus a system that automatically captures enquiries, sends follow-ups, and logs everything in a spreadsheet. Most clients start here.</div>
        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li>Custom website (up to 8 pages)</li>
          <li>AI lead capture system</li>
          <li>Automated email follow-ups</li>
          <li>Booking system integration</li>
          <li>Google Business setup</li>
          <li>Monthly performance report</li>
          <li>3 weeks delivery</li>
          <li class="no">CRM integration</li>
        </ul>
        <button class="pricing-btn solid" onclick="showPage('contact')">Most Popular</button>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="pricing-tier">Scale</div>
        <div class="pricing-price"><span>$</span>6,500</div>
        <div class="pricing-period">setup + $650/mo retainer</div>
        <div class="pricing-desc">The full setup — website, automation, CRM, SMS follow-ups, and monthly reporting. For businesses serious about scaling.</div>
        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li>Everything in Growth</li>
          <li>Full CRM setup & integration</li>
          <li>AI chatbot on website</li>
          <li>SMS follow-up sequences</li>
          <li>Review automation system</li>
          <li>A/B testing & optimisation</li>
          <li>Priority support</li>
          <li>Dedicated account manager</li>
        </ul>
        <button class="pricing-btn outline" onclick="showPage('contact')">Get Started</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="text-align:center;font-size:13px;color:var(--gray-600);margin-top:24px;font-weight:300;">Not sure what you need? Book a free call — we'll be straight with you about what makes sense for your business.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section>
    <div class="fade-in">
      <div class="label-tag">FAQ</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Questions we get<br>asked a lot.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list fade-in">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <h4>How long does it take to build my website?</h4>
          <div class="faq-icon">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Most websites are delivered within 2–3 weeks from the discovery call. More complex projects with full AI automation systems typically take 3–4 weeks. We'll give you a clear timeline before we start.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <h4>Do I need any technical knowledge?</h4>
          <div class="faq-icon">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>None at all. We handle everything — design, development, and automation setup. Once it's live, you just open your email or spreadsheet and your leads are there. No tech skills required.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <h4>What happens after the website is live?</h4>
          <div class="faq-icon">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>On the Growth and Scale plans, we monitor performance monthly and send you a report showing leads captured, conversion rates, and what we're improving. On Starter, we offer ongoing support at an hourly rate.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <h4>Can you work with my existing website?</h4>
          <div class="faq-icon">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. We can add AI automation and lead capture systems to your existing site without rebuilding it from scratch. Book a free audit and we'll assess what's possible.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <h4>Is there a contract or lock-in period?</h4>
          <div class="faq-icon">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>No lock-in contracts. The one-time fee covers the build, and monthly plans can be cancelled anytime with 30 days notice. We keep clients because of results, not contracts.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <h4>What industries do you work with?</h4>
          <div class="faq-icon">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>We specialise in local service businesses — gyms, clinics, barbershops, real estate agencies, trades, cafes, and more. If you rely on local customers, we can help.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <div class="final-cta fade-in">
